Public Resources Advisory Group, Inc. Key Developments

Rhode Island Selects Public Resources Advisory Group as Financial Advisor
Nov 18 15
Rhode Island announced that it has selected Public Resources Advisory Group as its financial advisor. The firm will advise the Rhode Island Treasury, Department of Administration, Office of Management and Budget and work closely with the state's bond counsel, rating agencies, trustees and other professionals involved in the state's financings.


