Company Summary


PRAG is proud of its history of providing clients with advice that has been based on an objective evaluation of their needs, whether structuring an issue, developing a plan of finance or assisting on a rating strategy. PRAG's clients reflect many long standing engagements, several for the entire 25 plus years of PRAG's existence. We believe PRAG's focus on client service and quantitative analysis has played a key role in our success over this period.









