Clients


The high frequency of our repeat engagements shows the quality of our service.  PRAG has served several clients including the City of Los Angeles, the State of New Hampshire, Baltimore County and the State of New York (Comptroller) since our founding in 1985, and we have advised many others such as the State of California, the State of Connecticut, the City of New York and the Commonwealth of Virginia for more than twenty years.
